Girl''\n* Untitled ''[[La Femme Nikita (TV series)|La Femme Nikita]]'' game\n* ''Oni 2: Death & Taxes''\n* ''S.W.A.T.''\n* Untitled [[Justice League]] game\n* ''Agent''\n\n== References ==\n{{Reflist|refs=\n<ref name=\"3-D Revolution\">{{cite book |url=https://books.google.com/books?id=k2Ajw-EEOEkC&pg=151 |title=3-D Revolution: The History of Modern Stereoscopic Cinema |first=Ray |last=Zone |date=July 6, 2012 |publisher=[[University Press of Kentucky]] |isbn=9780813136110 |page=151 |access-date=April 12, 2020 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200412114322/https://books.google.com/books?id=k2Ajw-EEOEkC&pg=151#v=onepage&q&f=false |archive-date=April 12, 2020 |url-status=live}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"ACE: Scenix\">{{cite magazine |url=https://archive.org/details/ACEIssue44May91/page/n33 |title=Shooting a Line |author= |magazine=[[ACE (magazine)|ACE]] |issue=44 |date=May 1991 |publisher=[[EMAP]] |pages=32\u201334 |access-date=December 10, 2018 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190113222314/https://archive.org/details/ACEIssue44May91/page/n33 |archive-date=January 13, 2019 |url-status=live}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"Adweek: Account acquisitions\">{{cite web |url=https://www.adweek.com/brand-marketing/account-acquisitions-br-clearnonebr-clearnonebr-clearnonebr-clearnonelos-3/ |title=Account Acquisitions: Los Angeles |author=Adweek Staff |date=August 2, 1993 |website=[[Adweek]] |access-date=November 19, 2017 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171201045917/http://www.adweek.com/brand-marketing/account-acquisitions-br-clearnonebr-clearnonebr-clearnonebr-clearnonelos-3/ |archive-date=December 1, 2017 |url-status=live}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"Ars Technica: Rockstar cleans house\">{{cite web |url=https://arstechnica.com/gaming/2010/07/rockstar-cleans-house-red-dead-redemption-team-axed/ |title=Rockstar cleans house, ''Red Dead Redemption'' team axed |first=Andrew |last=Webster |date=July 15, 2010 |website=[[Ars Technica]] |access-date=October 30, 2017 |archive