https://books.google.com/books?id=hxhmDQAAQBAJ&pg=274 |archive-date=February 15, 2019 |url-status=live}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"Polygon: Agent\">{{cite web |url=https://www.polygon.com/features/2019/2/21/18118822/agent-rockstar-san-diego |title=The Agent before Agent, a lost Rockstar San Diego project |first=Blake |last=Hester |date=February 21, 2019 |website=[[Polygon (website)|Polygon]] |access-date=September 26, 2019 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190730010547/https://www.polygon.com/features/2019/2/21/18118822/agent-rockstar-san-diego |archive-date=July 30, 2019 |url-status=live}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"Polygon: GTA V\">{{cite web |url=https://www.polygon.com/gaming/2012/5/30/3052089/rockstar-san-diego-collaborating-on-gta-v-employee-linkedin-uncovered |title=Rockstar San Diego collaborating on 'GTA V', employee Linkedin uncovered |author=emilygera |date=May 30, 2012 |website=[[Polygon (website)|Polygon]] |access-date=October 30, 2017 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171107011721/https://www.polygon.com/gaming/2012/5/30/3052089/rockstar-san-diego-collaborating-on-gta-v-employee-linkedin-uncovered |archive-date=November 7, 2017 |url-status=live}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"Polygon: How\">{{cite web |url=https://www.polygon.com/2018/10/17/17986118/how-the-red-dead-franchise-began-angel-studios-capcom-rockstar |title=How the Red Dead franchise began |first=Blake |last=Hester |date=October 17, 2018 |website=[[Polygon (website)|Polygon]] |access-date=October 21, 2018 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181021190823/https://www.polygon.com/2018/10/17/17986118/how-the-red-dead-franchise-began-angel-studios-capcom-rockstar |archive-date=October 21, 2018 |url-status=live}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"Publico: Oceania\">{{cite web |url=https://www.publico.pt/1999/04/12/jornal/a-loucura-da-microsoft-132029 |title=A loucura da Microsoft |language=pt |trans-title=The Microsoft Madness |first=Jos\u00e9 |last=Antunes |date=April 12, 1999 |website=[[P\u00fablico (Portugal)|P\u00fablico]] |access-date=April 12, 2020 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200412111530/https://www.publico.pt/1999/04/12/jornal/a-loucura-da-microsoft-132029 |archive-date=April 12, 2020 |url-status=live}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"Retro Gamer: Savage Quest\">{{cite web |url=https://www.retrogamer.net/retro_games90/savage-quest/ |title=Savage Quest |first=Ryan |last=Davies |date=December 4, 2008 |website=[[Retro Gamer]] |access-date=February 15, 2019 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190215202847/https://www.retrogamer.net/retro_games90/savage-quest/ |archive-date=February 15, 2019 |url-status=live}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"San Diego Source: Faraday lease\">{{cite web |url=http://www.sddt.com/News/article.cfm?SourceCode=20140825tdb |title=Rockstar renews Faraday lease in Carlsbad |author= |date=August 25, 2014 |website=[[San Diego Source]] |access-date=November 20, 2017 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171201043127/http://www.sddt.com/News/article.cfm?SourceCode=20140825tdb |archive-date=December 1, 2017 |url-status=live}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"San Diego U-T: Before the bubble\">{{cite web |url=http://www.signonsandiego.com/news/reports/survivors/index.html |title=Before the bubble |first=Bruce V. |last=Bigelow |date=August 19, 2001 |website=[[The San Diego Union-Tribune|SignOn San Diego]] |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20010913182325/http://www.signonsandiego.com/news/reports/survivors/index.html |archive-date=September 13, 2001 |url-status=dead}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"San Diego U-T: Rockstar conquers\">{{cite web |url=https://www.sandiegouniontribune.com/business/technology/sdut-red-2011feb27-htmlstory.html |title=Rockstar conquers another frontier |first=Tamara |last=Chuang |date=February 27, 2011 |website=[[The San Diego Union-Tribune]] |access-date=November 20, 2017 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171201033634/http://www.sandiegouniontribune.com/business/technology/sdut-red-2011feb27-htmlstory.html |archive-date